These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, gospel
House: craftsman, cottage, townhouse
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the craftsman house is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
5. the cottage house is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | soul | funk |
| House    | cottage    | townhouse | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, ritmeester
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, light-blue, fuchsia
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar       | alhambra | ritmeester | aristoff |
| Color   | fuchsia    | light-blue     | orange        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, milk
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, horse
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Beverage         | milk     | coffee | sprite |
| Pet   | rabbit | turtle     | horse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, june, february
1. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | tea | 7up  | iced-tea  |
| Birthday         | august  | june | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, western, disaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, climbing, tennis
1. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's sport is golf##2
2. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre         | horror   | disaster | western    |
| Sport   | climbing | tennis     | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, musician, electrician
1. the person drinking sprite is the musician##1
2. the electrician is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk | sprite   |
| Job   | electrician     | software-developer    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, cola
City: nizza, prague, boston
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person traveling to boston and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate | milk |
| City           | prague         | nizza         | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, green, turquise
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who likes ivory##2
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Color   | green | turquise | ivory |
| Sport    | parkour    | rowing | sailing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, zinnia
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, boat
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Flower   | zinnia   | poppy  | daisy  |
| Transport         | boat | train | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, bird, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Pet   | snake    | goat      | bird |
| Sport       | volleyball | snowboarding | lacrosse   |

