.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, malaysian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the mexican is the person drinking tea##1
3. the malaysian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | iced-tea | tea |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian   | mexican |

