.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, pink, blue
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, techno, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the person who likes black is the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
4. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Color   | blue | pink | black |
| Music-Genre     | techno     | country   | pop        |

