.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, water
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, salsa, disco
1. the person drinking water is between the person drinking 7up and the fan of salsa##2
2. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up | water | tea |
| Music-Genre     | trance    | disco  | salsa   |

