.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, journalist, police-officer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, baccarat
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the accountant is in the middle##1
3. the police-officer is the cain-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job         | police-officer | accountant   | journalist |
| Cigar   | cain   | davidoff | baccarat      |

