.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, rose
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | azalea | tulip | rose |
| Birthday   | january   | november          | october |

