.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, blend
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar     | alhambra  | blend   | oliveros |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice | iced-tea       |

 